# [Walkthrough - Local Hosting KlinikApp]

The KlinikApp has been successfully hosted locally.

## What was Accomplished
- **Infrastructure**: PostgreSQL and Redis are running in Docker containers.
- **Backend**: NestJS server is running at [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000).
- **Frontend**: Next.js server is running at [http://localhost:3001](http://localhost:3001).
- **Database**: Prisma migrations were applied and demo data was seeded (with minor non-critical conflicts resolved).

## Verification Results
- [x] **Backend Health**: Swagger documentation is accessible at [http://localhost:3000/api/docs](http://localhost:3000/api/docs).
- [x] **Frontend Health**: Next.js application is serving content at [http://localhost:3001](http://localhost:3001).

